item.dc:creator: @chassy13 Chassy13
item.description:
@chassy13 wrote:

How is it a command if you are going to be clicking the banana?

On delta sources, it would be located in the potions.java file. (potions class)

case #: //method break;

You will need to add the teleporting methods yourself into that packet. Replace the # with the ID of the banana.
